metadata.title: US OpenMind's BrainPack makes humanoid robots ‘real-world' smart
metadata.description: OpenMind's modular unit allows robots to perform advanced functions like self-guided patrols and real-time 3D mapping.
metadata.author: Bojan Stojkovski
metadata.keywords: AI, Automation, Autonomous Robots, Autonomy, brainpack, Fabric, OpenMind, Robotics, robots
